title: Sushibarinn
typeOfFood: Ovo, Japanese, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Takeaway sushi restaurant with a few tables, serving mainly fish but does have a vegetarian and a vegan plate. A few of the starters are vegan suitable such as edameme and soup. The staff will advise on what is okay. Food is made to-order.
